Kereta Api Indonesia Jobs: Few Positions
PT Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero) is the largest transportation service company in Indonesia which prioritizes professionalism and performance. Currently PT Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero) require professional candidates with high integrity to fill following positions:
Rekrutmen External Tingkat S1 2014
Requirements
Indonesian Citizen (WNI)
Maximum age by April 30, 2014 for Bachelor degree 35 years old
ADVERTISEMENT
Possess education diploma from State / Private University with minimum accreditation score on graduation A
Minimum GPA 2.95
Male, minimum height 160 cm
Not currently under employment bond (ikatan kerja langsung) with other instutions or PT Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero)
Well-behaved, required Police Notes (SKCK) from Police Department
Sound mind and body and not color blind
Free of illegal drugs or psychotropic
Not tattooed and pierced
Willing to be placed throughout the PT Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero) operational area
Required Documents
Legalized copy of Bachelor degree diploma
Legalized copy of Bachelor degree transcript
Copy of a valid National Identity Card (KTP)
Curriculum vitae, list all working experience in any agency, (skill / vocational) certificates, the highest diploma if any
Color photographs size 4X6 cm 4 pieces
Copy of Accreditation Certificate of the Department / Study Program on the date of graduation, from BAN PT and or legalized by the faculty / university
Application letter signed on the Rp. 6.000 stamp-duty
Drug-free certificate from the competent authority
A valid Police Notes (SKCK) from Police Department
Employment Certificate / working experience in any agency
Statement letter stated not currently under working bond (ikatan kerja langsung) with other instutions or PT Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero)
Selection Stages
Stage I : Document Screening
Stage II : Interviews
Stage III : Psychological Tests
Stage IV : Medical Check-Up
Application Procedures
Recruitment test will be held in: Semarang, Purwokerto, Yogyakarta dan Palembang
The applicant only allowed to apply in 1 location as listed above
The registration opened on May 6-7, 2014 at link below, the applicant should uploaded the required documents below on registration
Legalized copy of Bachelor degree diploma
Legalized copy of Bachelor degree transcript
Copy of a valid National Identity Card (KTP)
Curriculum vitae, list all working experience in any agency, (skill / vocational) certificates, the highest diploma if any
Color photographs size 4X6 cm 4 pieces
The documents screening result will be announced at link below on May 9, 2014
Interview will be conducted on May 10, 2014
Interview location based on the recruitment area
Other Provisions
ADVERTISEMENT
The selection process is free of charge and are encouraged to ignore those who promise to help in the selection process
The selection process using knockout system and the selection committee's decision can not be contested
Make sure all of the data uploaded immediately to be validated
Formation by Education
Bachelor degree in Civil Engineering (except majoring in Transportation)
Should you be interested and meet the requirements above please apply via link below.
